{"tid":49834,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"（驚嚇！）秦國差佬色誘搶匪","createTime":"2016-12-22T03:47:34.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-23T05:41:10.000Z","uid":29314,"like":21,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"3214a1e061bf010b9f852f0bda4670235f4ecbf0","tid":49834,"uid":29314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-22T03:47:34.000Z","msg":"泰國暖武裡府某段公路連續發生了多起摩托車搶劫案，並且女性受害者居多。為了能夠盡快破案，當地警局想出了讓警員男扮女裝「色誘」搶匪的奇招。<br />\r\n<br />\r\n這名名叫威萬的警察就成為了這次誘敵行為的主角，他穿上連身長裙與頭戴假髮，清晨5點手提女用包包在公車候車亭徘徊。<br />\r\n<br />\r\n結果劫犯真的「上鉤」了！警察發現有兩名年輕人騎摩托車在附近遊蕩觀察，但是意識到情況不對，很快逃離現場，不過最終兩人還是被警方抓獲。<br />\r\n<br />\r\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n\r<br />\n\r<br />\n<img src=\"https://s23.postimg.org/reohq384r/f99fb753_5859_624e_6ec4_e0510c3c6c3a.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs23.postimg.org%2Freohq384r%2Ff99fb753_5859_624e_6ec4_e0510c3c6c3a.jpg&h=2109a829&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"42df83ee515bde8fb004566cebf047046437b2c1","tid":49834,"uid":4525,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-22T03:49:11.000Z","msg":"你真識食"},{"pid":"20721453bec1d454a25b0cccf8e20243ba75ee46","tid":49834,"uid":20963,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-22T03:49:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/08.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/08.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6bd0ce936d5d0e94db28f2c437b9b4e234f327bf","tid":49834,"uid":29314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-22T03:50:37.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>你真識食</blockquote><br />\n唔怪得匪徒好快走左去啦"},{"pid":"342a7fd5b6d32a3407bddd4f88bc8b81124ef536","tid":49834,"uid":1713,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-22T03:51:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/25.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/25.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/25.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/fac